Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请勿以本片图利  否则亚美会惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以下的故事述说了在女孩们努力准备入学考试之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所发生的奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美少女战士Sailor Moon SuperS外传－亚美的初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}{\fs14}片源＆字幕制作：飞天圣明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是水野亚美  生日九月十日  处女座  血型A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兴趣只有读书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.53,0:01:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}{\fs14}校对：Switch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上我都会提早四十分钟到校读书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最爱的食物是三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}{\fs14}影片测试：Xelnaga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我可以边吃边读书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的颜色是水蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最擅长的运动是游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}{\fs14}后期：猫某人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最爱的科目是数学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我最不擅长的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情…情书…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～好痒～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  收到情书这种烦恼  我还真想要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西我收得不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我对它总是有奇怪的反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是反感吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行喔！　亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有句话不是这样说吗？“人生短暂  爱如战场”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  怎么？  不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该是“人生短暂  爱要及时”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那样讲也对…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这国中重要的最后一年  我们应该只专心在一件事情上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用功读书吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有错！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  在我的字典中  没有“恋爱”这两个字！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十二页…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十二页…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国模拟考的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名Mercury  五科总分五百分？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是每一科都满分！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mercury就是亚美吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  那是我登记考试结果的笔名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是…这个人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个满分的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅利克里斯（Mercurius）？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拉丁文的Mercury…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近  他一直在各补习班的模拟考中以满分紧跟着我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为他可能有意针对我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该不会是新的敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美…你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家或许是对的  可是我怎么这么在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅利克里斯…不知道是个怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国模拟考…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要是我多参加考试  多到补习班…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许会碰到梅利克里斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种悸动真是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个对手真棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～我一定会努力的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  第二天…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美有些不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉唉  这样是不是太过头了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～他又满分了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他每次都拿到满分！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能低估他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在说自己吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他到底是个怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想见见他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美  你好像…恋爱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  他可是我的对手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又说了一次“他”了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅利克里斯这名字也不见得是男生或女生  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  亚美你的理想对象是怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  我的理想对象  就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又聪明又英俊  像爱因斯坦一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  女孩们开始拟定计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的亚美可是第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那闪烁的双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女性化的举止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美的初恋！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～为了亚美  这就交给爱的女神爱野美奈子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟露个肩膀一样容易
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅利克里斯的身分  要查出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？  看来小兔想到什么主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈琉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海野要预测下次考试会考什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海野…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我脸上？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海野！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！  到了这种时候  我就只能靠你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模拟考中用梅利克里斯当笔名的人你认识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙？  他是我的朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海野！  你没事吧  海野？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时亚美正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会征服这个补习班的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你没事吧？  别太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的  梅利克里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力用功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力用功！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力用功！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微小睡一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力用功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力用功！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续努力用功！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睡一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把整堂课都睡掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}{\pos(225,160)}{\frz32}(Mercurius)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这苏醒的欲望与悸动的气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！  坠入情网的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅利克里斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有办法不想那个男生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我地灵做这种事情已经有上百年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会饱餐一顿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心！  她会蚕食别人的欲望！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头好重…感冒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里  那家伙上的补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很破  不过是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  梅利克里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  曲眼博士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲眼博士是我用的笔名  曲曲～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美的情况变糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…身体动不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅利克里斯  这也是你做的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经被欲望给操控了  时候到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有欲望的源头  情书攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人可以抵抗初恋情书中的甜言蜜语！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情…情…情书～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为考试准备的方程式还有背书  都从头中跑走了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅利克里斯的身分  该不该讲出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在滴咕什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行～不行～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的知识都从你的脑中跑走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你马上就要变成笨蛋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  虚弱到看不清了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是梅利克里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真卑鄙！  我的头痛  在补习班睡觉  都是你搞的鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…哈啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会认输的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水星水晶力量 变身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模拟考结果＋补习班＋压力的根源（阻碍／对手）\N＝梅利克里斯＝敌人＝击倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到第一名而不择手段  不可原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱与考试的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手服美少女战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手水星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的头浸到水里  好好反省吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他又不是梅利克里斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直明白你是敌人  却仍然让你跑到头脑里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  对手之间的胜负之争就要结束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看看水星的胜利方程式！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水星…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之狂想曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美  没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到头来我还是没能看到他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手等于敌人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我的成绩不会好到那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为美奈你没必要担心...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让亚美知道梅利克里斯的身分！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不知道还比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看到他了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像…像这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  现在超人气的明星！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像年轻时的爱因斯坦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我的对手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有点过头了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  要是她知道其实他长得像海野一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会用梅利克里斯这个名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来说明！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}{\pos(105,130)}(Su Ri Ku Ru Me)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}{\pos(255,130)}(Mercurius)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是把“数理魔人”反过来念
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:13:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  梅利克里斯还在  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚美那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他留给我对付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“他”？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  高标准的Mercury  继续她的战斗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:36.64,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,La La La never give up！  继续努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:36.64,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ラララネバーギブアップ！　がんばるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:40.68,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了此刻全心全意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:40.68,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このショウブにかけてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.62,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期盼的热情加速了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.62,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ウキウキ　トキメクの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:51.69,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春时总是可以重绘爱的轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:51.69,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思春期エイジ  かきかえＯＫ  恋するプロフィール
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:07.13,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后  我对一位偷心者一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:07.13,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きいて放课后のトリックスター  ひとめぼれなのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:15.13,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如过往的情人  乱了我的情绪  但我不想再度伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:15.13,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前の彼とにてる  くるくるまわる　またキズつくかな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.82,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办？  但我已经决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:18.82,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしよう？　でもきめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.90,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要陪他玩玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.90,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わざとじらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:31.55,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘扬于风中的水手服  我将毫不保留的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:31.55,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,セーラー服なびかせて  “らしく”いきましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:37.23,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,La La La never give up！  继续努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:37.23,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ラララネバーギブアップ！　がんばるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:41.29,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次将轮到我出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:41.29,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんどこそ　私の番
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:45.31,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧张的悸动加速了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:45.31,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ　トキメクの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:52.61,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青春时总是可以重绘爱的轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:52.61,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思春期エイジ　かきかえＯＫ  恋するプロフィール
